  "prompt": "Which is the best coaching centre for IBPS-PO preparation in Varanasi?",
  "response": "Selecting the best coaching center for IBPS-PO preparation in Varanasi can depend on various factors such as teaching methodology, faculty experience, infrastructure, batch size, and student reviews. Some of the popular coaching centers in Varanasi that are known for banking exam preparation include:\n\n1. **Bankers Adda** - Known for its comprehensive study materials and mock tests.\n2. **Career Launcher** - Offers extensive courses for bank exams with experienced faculty.\n3. **Time Institute** - Renowned for its structured course and regular updates on exam patterns.\n4. **Mahendra\u2019s Institute** - Popular for its wide reach and experienced trainers.\n\nIt\u2019s best to visit these coaching centers, attend demo classes, and check reviews from former students before making a decision. Make sure the center aligns with your learning style and preparation needs.",
